children.description: When I open submenu Company Management of menu Common
And In Company management screen, I fill value 'CIJ' for filter in column 'Company name'
And In Company management screen, I select row '0'
And I edit company with name Test company

And I input company detail as below
| companyFullName | workType | listed | headOffice | customerCode | branches | website |
| Test company | 土木 | Type One | 岩手県 | z999 | 静岡県, 岡山県 | anlh2207@gmail.com |
